<A HREF="http://www.charite.de/">
Charit&#233;
</A>) have pioneered 2D-electrophoresis technology for 
proteins. We now propose to apply this experience to plants 
and indeed to agriculturally-important crops. Developing such 
technologies for plants, initially for the model plant 
<I>Arabidopsis
</I> and later on for crop plants is the goal of this 
project. 
